{
  "texts": [
    "Machine learning techniques were applied to analyze a dataset of 14,251 COVID-19 cases to identify potential virus cases.In [37] an IoT architecture was proposed to detect the infected person.",
    "Smart sensors and IoT are being used to measure and record body signs.",
    "Individuals' temperatures aid in identifying those who are affected.",
    "In addition, it assists in maintaining social distance.",
    "Healthcare systems incorporating IoT technology can improve decision-making by utilizing cloud computing and data analysis.Authors [38] demonstrated an IoT-based method for preventing COVID-19 in the workplace."
  ]
}